HowTo(s) / JRC-GFOSS
====================

This is the web page of the gfoss-jrc group. We use it for uploading code and receipts on how to do things with GFOSS, such as GRASS GIS, R, Python, etc. For more information about the group and its activities see the [wiki](https://github.com/gfoss-jrc/mainrepo/wiki).
